article_title: Ridgeview offers Walk-In Clinic for mental health care

article_metadata.description: Ridgeview Behavioral Health Services Inc. has announced the introduction of a Walk-In Clinic at its Anderson County office at 240 W. Tyrone Road in Oak Ridge.
